John Lord, 86, went missing from his home on April 6 less than a week after his wife June, 81, died from a 'catastrophic bleed' to the brain . 
  Family feared the worst after he left a note describing how he missed his wife of 63 years . 
  Body pulled from River Trent on April 15 was sadly that of Mr Lord . 
  Family believe he jumped from bridge at 'special place' where they used to take romantic walks . 
 